The Ibiza season is nearly upon us as we unleash our timely second volume to our Ibiza Club Anthems series. This is all about the cream of the underground rubbing shoulder to shoulder with the nu breed of exciting producers to deliver an audio explosion guaranteed to take the roof off of any party. From the gorgeous piano intro from Hulsmans and Greening all the way through to Micheal Lees turbo charged remix at the climax this album delivers at every level. The track list speaks for itself including, Manuel le Saux, Datt, Kearney, Lostly, Hardwick and many more.
